OG Windows vibe, came before Win11

Super stable & compatible AF

Editions: Home, Pro, Enterprise, Education, LTSC

32-bit & 64-bit versions (32-bit = older PCs)

Feature updates: 20H2 → 21H1 → 21H2 → 22H2

Runs almost everything: apps, games, software

Start menu + taskbar = classic Windows feel

Virtual desktops + Snap = multitasking made easy

Microsoft Store = apps, games, media

Security squad: Windows Hello, BitLocker, Defender Antivirus

Gaming ready: DirectX 12, Game Mode, Xbox integration

Fresh install, upgrade, or VM = all supported

LTSC / Enterprise = no bloat, ultra-stable for long-term

Fast boot, smooth UI

Lightweight for older PCs

Long support till Oct 2025

